## RULES

- Background `#F2ECE4` — no section color change
- No blue filled buttons — closing link is text-link only
- Competitor images: `filter: grayscale(35%) opacity(0.75)` — editorial, not mocking
- CrownCalm ✓ symbols: `pillar.textColor` (phase color) — not a flat color
- Phase color bars on row left edge: same 4px bar from S4 spec tags
- `border-left` + `border-right` on CrownCalm column: `rgba(26,26,26,0.10)` — subtle column highlight
- Never name actual competitor brands — categories only
- `partial` label appears only on cells where result is `'partial'`
- Summary row `5/5` for CrownCalm is the visual punchline — make it legible
- Grid rule lines match all previous sections exactly
- Animate only `opacity`, `transform` — no width/height animation

